Process called "transfer_knowledge_via_analogy" that takes graph as KnowledgeGraph and mappings as List[Dictionary] returns List[String]:
    Return list containing nothing

Process called "validate_slot_constraints" that takes value as Any and constraints as List[Dictionary] returns List[String]:
